name: Flavorah
description: Flavorah is super concentrated flavoring made for DIY ejuice.   Unlike other concentrated flavors available on the internet that were formulated for candy and baking, Flavorah's uniquely crafted flavor notes and high potency make it the real choice for flavoring vapor.  Give our flavors a try in a new ejuice formula, or to update a recipe that needs to be distinct and flawless.
